summary: The code uses Assimp library to convert .dae files (Assimp Scene format) into .obj files (Wavefront 3D Object file). It performs the conversion for both "head.dae" and "head_camera.dae", saving the results as "head.obj" and "head_camera.obj" respectively.

details.comment: The code uses Assimp library to convert .dae files (Assimp Scene format) into .obj files (Wavefront 3D Object file). It performs the conversion for both "head.dae" and "head_camera.dae", saving the results as "head.obj" and "head_camera.obj" respectively.
details.content:
assimp export head.dae head.obj
assimp export head_camera.dae head_camera.obj
